            <h3>Do I need an account to use Bolt Personal?</h3>
            <p>No. Bolt Personal runs entirely on your machine with no login. Just download, add an AI API key, and start using.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item">
            <h3>What happens after the 7-day Enterprise trial?</h3>
            <p>The app stops connecting to enterprise features (email, calendar, agentic actions). Your local data remains. Contact us to purchase a license or switch to Personal edition.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item">
            <h3>What AI keys work?</h3>
            <p>Any OpenAI-compatible API &mdash; OpenAI, Anthropic, Google Gemini (has a free tier), Ollama (local), Groq, Together, or your own endpoint.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item">
            <h3>Does Bolt send my data anywhere?</h3>
            <p>No. Both editions run fully on your device. AI requests go directly from your machine to your chosen provider &mdash; nothing routes through Sparcle.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item">
            <h3>What IDP credentials do I need for Enterprise Trial?</h3>
            <p>Your organization's OAuth Client ID and Secret for Google Workspace, Microsoft Entra ID, Okta, or any OIDC provider. The setup wizard walks you through it step by step.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item">
            <h3>What is demo mode?</h3>
